snippet.title: iMode Mo Issho - PS1 Gameplay Footage (Real PS1 Hardware)
snippet.description:
Here is the only footage online of i-Mode Mo Issho for the Sony PlayStation 1.
This game Requires a PS1+PocketStation+Save file from the Game Doko Demo Issyo before it will even begin.
This footage was captured on a PS2 via Component cables.
